Class SinglyLinkedList.Node<E>

java.lang.Object
advds.assignment1.dataStructures.SinglyLinkedList.Node<E>
Type Parameters:
E - the element type
Enclosing class:
SinglyLinkedList<E>
private static class SinglyLinkedList.Node<E> extends Object
Node of a singly linked list, which stores a reference to its element and to the subsequent node in the list (or null if this is the last node).
